JOIN EMAIL CLUB Home About Us About Us Player Development Course Layout Course Views Book A Tee Time Events Memberships Hole In One Club Contact Us Contact Us Email Club Directions Donation Request Employment Opportunities About Us Eagle Dunes Golf Club When Eagle Dunes Golf Club opened its course in 2003 in Sorrento, Florida, it greatly pleased those who have a passion for golf and it quickly earned a reputation as being an enjoyable 18-hole course with few crowds. Mike Dasher created the 7024 yard, par 72 course to challenge and excite golfers while still making it fun for all skill levels. Eagle Dunes has received great praise from many golfers since its opening. Golfers appreciate its elevation changes, well maintained greens and beautiful fairways. Golf Digest gave Eagle Dunes a four star rating in the 2008-2009 edition of Golf Digest’s “Best Places to Play.” Rates Weekdays- $39.00 – $37.00 + tax After 11:00am- $34.00 – $32.00 + tax After 2:00pm- $29.00 – $25.00 + tax After 4:00pm- $20.00 + tax Weekends- $49.00 – $46.00 After 11:00am- $42.00 – $38.00 + tax After 2:00pm- $32.00 – $30.00 + tax After 4:00pm- $22.00 + tax ( *9 Hole Rates AFTER 2:00pm ONLY $20.00 + tax) About Us Eagle Dunes Golf Club When Eagle Dunes Golf Club opened its course in 2003 in Sorrento, Florida, it greatly pleased those who have a passion for golf and it quickly earned a reputation as being an enjoyable 18-hole course with few crowds. JOIN EMAIL CLUB Home About Us About Us Player Development Course Layout Course Views Book A Tee Time Events Memberships Hole In One Club Contact Us Contact Us Email Club Directions Donation Request Employment Opportunities Memberships Membership Programs Unlimited Golf Membership: We are now offering Unlimited Golf Membership. The program allows unlimited golf anytime Monday through Thursday and after 11:00 a.m. Friday through Sunday including holidays. Members of the program will also receive a large basket of range balls every day to allow them to work on their golf game and enjoy their improvements on the golf course. This program must be paid in advance and a minimum of 6 months purchased. $400.00 + tax per month for a single person $450.00 + tax per month for a family Eagle Dunes Email Program: Please don’t forget to leave us your e-mail address at the clubhouse to receive our periodic e-mails including discount coupons. Junior Program $25.00 per adult: Juniors under 15 years of age play for free after 3:00 p.m. every day when accompanied by a paid adult (one junior per each paid adult). Player Pass Discount Card Program $199.99 (+ tax) per year: The card is good for a $5.00 discount anytime Monday through Thursday and after 11:00 Friday through Sunday. The card also includes many additional benefits. Player Pass Membership Program $395.00 (+ tax) per year: This membership is good for discounts anytime you play and include limited free range balls, a USGA handicap program, discounts on merchandise, and many additional benefits. Player Development Program $75.00 (+tax) per month: This program serves as a range plan and includes one medium basket of range balls per day. ($360.00 monthly value). Range balls must be used the same day they are received. (This program must be paid in advance and a minimum of 6 months purchased). Free Instructional Clinics: These clinics will be available on certain Saturdays and will cover all aspects of the golf game. Please contact the golf shop for more information and to register for a clinic. All rates listed are plus tax and are subject to change without notice. The summer specials and unlimited golf membership will expire at designated times. Please ask the golf shop staff for additional details on all programs and specials.
